  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To investigate the diagnostic value of ultralow-dose computed tomography in the detection of
      pulmonary nodules and lung parenchym alterations (e.g. emphysema) compared to
      standard-dose-CT.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
